&"next_id": "53",
&"text": "img: suzanna/2",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"53": {
&"character": "Caleb",
&"id": "53",
&"next_id": "54",
&"text": "Looks like a nice start to her night",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"54": {
&"character": "Caleb",
&"id": "54",
&"next_id": "55",
&"text": "She's really pretty isn't she?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"55": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "55",
&"next_id": "56",
&"text": "She is!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"56": {
&"character": "Caleb",
&"id": "56",
&"next_id": "57",
&"text": "It's a good picture too",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"57": {
&"character": "Caleb",
&"id": "57",
&"next_id": "58",
&"text": "Makes you think what kind of person the guy is when they're out of frame!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"58": {
&"character": "Caleb",
&"id": "58",
&"next_id": "59",
&"text": "Let's see what else there was",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"59": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "59",
&"next_id": "60",
&"text": "img: suzanna/3",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"6": {
&"character": "Caleb",
&"id": "6",
&"next_id": "7",
&"text": "Got anything in mind for a submission?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"60": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "60",
&"next_id": "61",
&"text": "This one too",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"61": {
&"character": "Caleb",
&"id": "61",
&"next_id": "62",
&"text": "She didn't recognize you so you were able to get pretty close!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"62": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "62",
&"next_id": "63",
&"text": "She did not look like she's having a good time 😓",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"63": {
&"character": "Caleb",
&"id": "63",
&"next_id": "64",
&"text": "Yeah, we'll probably hear about this tomorrow 😟",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"64": {
&"character": "Caleb",
&"id": "64",
&"next_id": "65",
&"text": "Ms Suzanna is quite open with these things, maybe even a little too open sometimes 😅",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"65": {
&"character": "Caleb",
&"id": "65",
&"next_id": "66",
&"text": "All her confidence comes back though and she tries again when we root for her!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"66": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "66",
&"next_id": "67",
&"text": "That's great to hear",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"67": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "67",
&"next_id": "68",
&"text": "But was it okay to take pictures of her like this, while she's so down?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"68": {
&"character": "Caleb",
&"id": "68",
&"next_id": "69",
&"text": "I thought the same at first but I showed her a picture similar to this and it really brightened up her day",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
