raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"forest_trail\")
Caleb: Hey!
Player: Hey Caleb
Caleb: I'll be there soon
do echo_set([\"78\"])
Caleb: Got anything in mind for a submission?
Player: Not really! Hoping you could fill me in
Caleb: No worries, I can do that
Caleb: What I like to do is pick a spot and find someone interesting
Caleb: I like to try to snapshot them in that moment
Player: Almost like a wildlife photographer lol
Caleb: Exactly! 
Caleb: I like to try to understand people and their story and struggles and display them in the work
Caleb: With some limits of course, we shouldn't stalk or bother anyone!
Caleb: There are some good places for us to check out
Caleb: I recommend the beach or the city
Caleb: Both are good options
- Beach
	Player: Beach sounds like a nice peaceful location
	Caleb: It really is!
- City
	set Story.flag = \"CitySubmission\"
	Player: City might have some good stories to tell
	Caleb: Quite a lot going on in the city
	Caleb: We'll definitely find something
Caleb: Alright almost there, we can meet at your station in 5 minutes
do echo_clear()
Player: Sounds good!
do advance_time(3, 5)
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Caleb: Good job with the pictures today!
Caleb: You got some really good ones!
Player: Thanks
if Story.has_flag(\"CitySubmission\"):
	Caleb: I still can't believe we ran into Professor Suzanna
	Player: Mabel's professor right?
	Caleb: Yup, and she's our club sponsor!
else:
	Caleb: I still can't believe we ran into Alice
	Player: This was that girl that hides out in the Photography Club room right?
	Caleb: Yeah 😅
	Caleb: Because she gets picked on, poor thing
	Caleb: Naomi actually convinced her to join the club
	Player: Oh that's interesting
	Caleb: Yep so she'll be a new member hopefully!
Caleb: But what a coincidence huh?
Player: Unexpected for sure!
Caleb: We took some pretty good pictures of her
Caleb: Let's go through what we have now for a submission then
if Story.has_flag(\"CitySubmission\"):
	Player: Sure thing
	Player: img: suzanna/2
	Caleb: Looks like a nice start to her night
	Caleb: She's really pretty isn't she?
	Player: She is! 
	Caleb: It's a good picture too
	Caleb: Makes you think what kind of person the guy is when they're out of frame!
	Caleb: Let's see what else there was
	Player: img: suzanna/3
	Player: This one too
	Caleb: She didn't recognize you so you were able to get pretty close!
	Player: She did not look like she's having a good time 😓
	Caleb: Yeah, we'll probably hear about this tomorrow 😟
	Caleb: Ms Suzanna is quite open with these things, maybe even a little too open sometimes 😅
	Caleb: All her confidence comes back though and she tries again when we root for her!
	Player: That's great to hear
	Player: But was it okay to take pictures of her like this, while she's so down?
	Caleb: I thought the same at first but I showed her a picture similar to this and it really brightened up her day
	Caleb: She told me that after seeing the picture, she no longer thought of it as \"the worst day of her life\"
	Caleb: I took some pictures myself that I'm going to show her afterwards, I'm sure they'll cheer her up!
	Player: That's a relief!
	Caleb: You have one more right?
	Player: img: suzanna/4
	Player: That's the last one!
	Caleb: This one is so good
	Caleb: Really poetic don't you think?
	Player: Really sad yeah
	Caleb: I wish I took this one cause then I could show her right away!
	Caleb: But I think this is perfect for your submission
	Caleb: And if she looks through the submissions herself, she'll probably see this anyway!
	Caleb: But I got some nice ones too I can show her 😁
	Player: Phew that was an interesting experience
	Caleb: Glad you thought so!
	do queue_social_post(\"suzanna_city_evening\")
else:
	Player: This is the first one I took
	Player: img: alice/2
	Caleb: I've actually never seen Alice smile!
	Caleb: She has a rough time in college
	Caleb: But seems like she's at peace here
	Player: Yeah
	Caleb: Good thing she didn't notice us
	Caleb: I didn't wanna bother her alone time but these pictures are so pretty
	Caleb: This is basically what it's like being in the photography club
	Caleb: Usually there's a given task or event though that we go out to record
	Caleb: Sometimes it'll be modeling shoots too
	Player: Oh sounds like a lot of variety
	Caleb: It is
	Caleb: You'll never get bored
	Caleb: You have the other ones btw?
	Player: Oh right
	Player: img: alice/3
	Caleb: This one came out nicely too!
	Caleb: Not gonna lie, I kinda wanted to take a swim after seeing this haha
	Player: The weather was great!
	Caleb: Yep!
	Caleb: Show me that last one
	Player: img: alice/4
	Player: Here
	Caleb: This one's probably the perfect submission
	Caleb: Pictures that really make you think are always good
	Player: I agree
	Player: Were these okay to take though?
	Caleb: I'm gonna show the ones I took to Naomi and see if we can somehow cheer Alice up
	Caleb: I want her to have a better time in college and these might just clue us in on what we can do for her
	Player: That's sounds nice!
	Caleb: Thanks 😄 I do what I can to help
Caleb: Alright then
Caleb: You don't have to worry about the application process
Caleb: Since we're a pretty small club, I can submit yours directly to Naomi who handles all the paperwork
Player: Wow convenient!
Caleb: delete: What are friends for!
Caleb: Ah didn't want to assume anything but happy to help!
- I think of you as a friend!
	set Story.flag = \"CalebFriend\"
	Player: I think of you as a friend!
	Caleb: 😁 Awesome, I do too!
	Caleb: I can't wait to make this all official so our little band of friends grows!
	Caleb: Group chat's been a little quiet lately haha
- Thanks!
	Player: Thanks!
Caleb: Alright, gotta go put this together
Caleb: Be seeing you!
Player: Good night!
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
